{
  "stem": "25598.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So that was impossible to retrieve, because that was public and you don't-- you don't risk that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "However, the stuff in the attic remained intact.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It didn't dawn on anybody that there's something in there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And it was a lifesaver, because there weren't any needles after the war, because all the metal-- I think-- I don't know what metal exactly needles are made-- made from, but whatever they're made from was not available because of the war.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And people-- I mean, you could get food for three days for a bloody needle, which was-- it was fantastic.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "The flour, the soap, the toothpaste, everything was intact, just the way he left it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But the needles were the real treasure.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "That was-- that was very, very important.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And then, of course, Romania turned communist.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And after having gone through the camps, the theory of communism was very appealing to me as a teenager.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "My mother sort of had a leftist orientation from the Zionist organization, so now she became even more.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And the-- the thing was that the only way this is never going to happen again is if we all become communist.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And then we're all brothers and then we're all equal and all the bullshit which never happened.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And I became very actively involved in the communist youth organization.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And I had a lot of organizing skill since I was small.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And I honed them, and I became a member of the Central Committee, and I was traveling to Bucharest.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And I was-- I mean, I was a kid, but I was doing things which were pretty adult.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And-- and I remained very hooked on communism until I finished university, this-- because the school system also brainwashes you every minute.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
